#: includes/class-content.php:54
msgid "Search by meaning, not keywords…"
msgstr "Busca por significado, no por palabras clave…"

#: includes/class-content.php:55
msgid "Describe an idea, theme, or event…"
msgstr "Describe una idea, un tema o un suceso…"

#: includes/class-content.php:56
msgid "What kind of story are you after?"
msgstr "¿Qué tipo de historia buscas?"

#: includes/class-content.php:57
msgid "Try a concept, a trend, or a mood…"
msgstr "Prueba con un concepto, una tendencia o un estado de ánimo…"

#: includes/class-content.php:58
msgid "Ask for what you want, not what it’s called…"
msgstr "Pide lo que quieres, no cómo se llama…"

#: includes/class-content.php:59
msgid "What are you curious about today?"
msgstr "¿Sobre qué sientes curiosidad hoy?"

#: includes/class-content.php:60
msgid "Type a theme, not a keyword…"
msgstr "Escribe un tema, no una palabra clave…"

#: includes/class-content.php:61
msgid "Tell it like you’d tell a friend…"
msgstr "Cuéntalo como se lo contarías a un amigo…"

#: includes/class-content.php:62
msgid "Think fuzzy, not exact…"
msgstr "Piensa en impreciso, no en exacto…"

#: includes/class-content.php:63
msgid "A feeling, a trend, a half-remembered headline…"
msgstr "Una sensación, una tendencia, un titular a medio recordar…"

#: includes/class-content.php:64
msgid "Be vague. We’ll figure it out…"
msgstr "Sé impreciso. Ya nos entenderemos…"

#: includes/class-content.php:65
msgid "Explain it like I’m a database…"
msgstr "Explícamelo como si fuera una base de datos…"

#: includes/class-content.php:66
msgid "We accept mumbles…"
msgstr "Aceptamos murmullos…"

#: includes/class-content.php:67
msgid "Don’t overthink it. Just type…"
msgstr "No le des tantas vueltas. Solo escribe…"

#: includes/class-content.php:68
msgid "Type a hunch…"
msgstr "Escribe una corazonada…"

#: includes/class-content.php:69
msgid "Whisper an idea into the void…"
msgstr "Susurra una idea al vacío…"

#: includes/class-content.php:70
msgid "Close enough works here…"
msgstr "Aquí vale casi cualquier cosa…"

#: includes/class-content.php:71
msgid "Bring your loosest query…"
msgstr "Trae tu consulta más vaga…"

#: includes/class-content.php:72
msgid "Describe, don’t define…"
msgstr "Describe, no definas…"

#: includes/class-content.php:73
msgid "Ask it like a human, not a SQL query…"
msgstr "Pregunta como un humano, no como una consulta SQL…"

#: includes/class-rest.php:67
msgid "Too many requests, slow down."
msgstr "Demasiadas solicitudes, por favor espera un momento."

